{"type": "article", "id": 2402, "title": "Alessi Ovale 系列餐具", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-17T00:09:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 2, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232359Z6J1aju8K7nQg4vE.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tBouroullec兄弟 2012 年为意大利品牌 Alessi 设计了 Ovale 系列餐具，将 Alessi 擅长的金属加工工艺进一步放大，齐全的不锈钢刀叉餐具系列分类细微，甚至还备有专用的 13 厘米咖啡调羹以及 11 厘米的摩卡咖啡调羹等，粗陶瓷餐具系列则以简约典雅的设计取胜，浅粉以及浅灰的选择透出淡雅精致的味道。现任 Alessi 掌门人Alberto Alessi 将这个系列的产品形容为“精致，简单，接近一种新的原始主义”。定价 16.5 至 495 欧元不等，<a href=\"http://store.alessi.com/ita/it-it/catalog/detail/ovale-servizio-di-posate/reb09?ic=udmc1g%3D%3D\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232357Tt1RULkIPzEd8SHn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232358o78YMwKCW2Tirhlz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6734375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052323583IEMv4geoA5QTlkO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}